{"tid":2372684,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Zack Snyder導演剪輯版[Justice League: The Snyder Cut]宣佈改採上映型式","createTime":"2021-01-20T01:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T06:49:59.000Z","uid":218407,"like":12,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"45a22c06c12550b0fc71cf4c1fc7956d2a41d82e","tid":2372684,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T01:25:41.000Z","msg":"好似仲未有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nZack Snyder 重新打造的導演剪輯版《正義聯盟 Justice League》於上月底透露正在努力登上院線，且會以 R 級/限制級電影形式上映。近日，Zack Snyder 意外在與網民的互動之中，突襲宣佈本片將改變上映型式，預計會以長達 4 小時的電影規格登場。<br />\n<br />\n過去《Justice League: The Snyder Cut》設定是將全片切分為四集迷你影集於 HBO Max 平台獨家上映，如今 Zack Snyder 於 Vero 平台中被網民問道本片會是一部影集還是電影？導演簡潔有力地回應：「One Shot.」<br />\n<br />\n如此即能呼應到 Zack Snyder 為何堅持希望本片能在電影院上映，而 Zack 也為本片的重新上映進行部分補拍，尤其是前任「Joker」Jared Leto 的加入更是引人關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2021/1/zack-snyder-confirms-justice-league-four-hours-runtime\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2021%2F1%2Fzack-snyder-confirms-justice-league-four-hours-runtime&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=f85c9771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2021/1/zack-snyder-confirms-justice-league-four-hours-runtime</a><br />\n<br />\n希望到時戲院準時有開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以俾我係咁已刷返10次咁大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004ee1ef6f836cbc7b1a21ea9e1db60036a4092b","tid":2372684,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T01:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat